                        My daughter runs the family business, but all my children are owners—what happens when
                        I’m gone?
                    


                        I handle almost everything for my adult child---who will do that when I’m unable?
                    


                        How can I pass wealth to my family instead of the IRS?
                    


                        I want to leave a legacy to benefit my hometown forever.
                    


                        How can I ensure that I invest my gas royalties wisely?
                    


                        Our extended family’s lakeside lodge is a treasured vacation spot for everyone, but
                        I’ve always looked after it. No one else lives nearby---how can we keep it going after
                        I’m gone?
                    




