Vision, Integrity and Trust










About Us

                        Privately owned and independent, Security National serves as your family’s “central office”, and
                        yet we also work with many individual clients. Whether it’s expert investment
                        management, tax-savvy transition of wealth to the next generation, charitable planning and
                        endowment services, looking after treasured family properties, or helping
                        transition shares of the family business, Security National’s experienced team makes the
                        difference for you and your loved ones.

                        Our work begins with a conversation. At Security National, we know that to empower clients we
                        first need to listen. We then bring to bear diverse resources. Analytical tools
                        help, but it is the insights, experience, and good judgement of our people that gets you where
                        you want to be.
                    








