Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Instl Trust, Fiduciary & Custody
Security National Trust Company operates as a trust company. The Company provides personal trust, estate settlement, investment management, retirement plans, and endowments, and financial planning services. Security National Trust serves customers in the States of West Virginia and Pennsylvania.




