Company Overview of The Security National Bank And Trust Co.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of August 20, 2008, The Security National Bank And Trust Co. was acquired by The Park National Bank Inc. The Security National Bank And Trust Co. provides banking products and services. It offers personal checking accounts, savings accounts, loans, credit cards, 24/7 banking, and other services; and business depository services, business savings accounts, commercial loans, public funds/entities, business card services, 24/7 banking, onsite express deposits, automated clearing house services, lockbox services, positive pay, and retirement plan services. The company also offers trust and investment services. The Security National Bank And Trust Co. was formerly known as The Security Nationa...
As of August 20, 2008, The Security National Bank And Trust Co. was acquired by The Park National Bank Inc. The Security National Bank And Trust Co. provides banking products and services. It offers personal checking accounts, savings accounts, loans, credit cards, 24/7 banking, and other services; and business depository services, business savings accounts, commercial loans, public funds/entities, business card services, 24/7 banking, onsite express deposits, automated clearing house services, lockbox services, positive pay, and retirement plan services. The company also offers trust and investment services. The Security National Bank And Trust Co. was formerly known as The Security National Bank (Springfield, OH) and changed its name to The Security National Bank And Trust Co. in May 1979. The company was founded in 1915 and is based in Springfield, Ohio with additional offices in Mechanicsburg, North Lewisburg, Urbana, Enon, Medway, New Carlisle, South Charleston, Springfield, Jamestown, Xenia, Plain City, and Springboro, Ohio.
Detailed Description


40 South Limestone StreetSpringfield, OH 45502United StatesFounded in 1915



