Security National Trust Company Entry Level Jobs and Internships





















































Follow








Security National Trust Company

                Formed in 1999 by HB&W, Inc, Security National Trust Company, nationally chartered, is committed to meet and exceed customer expectations in the careful administration of financial services. We continue to build upon the combined trust experience of our staff of over 180 years.  

Security National Trust Company is a full service fiduciary that serves individuals, non profit organizations and other businesses relating to the following services: 


Personal Trust Services 
Investment Management 
Employee Benefit Services 
Foundations and Endowments 


Security National Trust Company believes in developing products to meet the needs of our clients, not a prepackaged array of in-house money market funds and mutual funds. We believe in traditional values and that is why you will always reach a friendly voice. Security National Trust Company is committed to answering your questions and fulfilling your requests immediately with the information you need. 

We look forward to provide you with a full range of Trust and Investment Services and invite you to call our Wheeling, West Virginia office at 1-877-768-7878 or our Lancaster, Pennsylvania office at 1-866-454-9383. 

                                    
